udAharaNe, guNoVtatxra $2$, gaCaCx $20$, sarayxdhana $1048575$ Agalu aMtayx padaveSuTx?


\qq $104875\times {20-1} \above 0pt {\qquad2}$ $\left( \tfrac{\qquad2-1}{\quad\quad20-1} \quad\above 0pt {2} \right)$ $=524288.$

